        | 05 iw                                      | ADD AX, imm16                              | I                                          | RW, R                                      |                                            | E.OF E.SF E.ZF E.AF E.CF E.PF              |                                            |                                            |                                            | V                                          | V                                          |                                            | addw                                       |                                            | Add imm16 to AX.
