        | 00 /r                                      | ADD r/m8, r8                               | MR                                         | RW, R                                      |                                            | E.OF E.SF E.ZF E.AF E.CF E.PF              |                                            |                                            |                                            | V                                          | V                                          |                                            | addb                                       | YES                                        | Add r8 to r/m8.
